The Nigerian Army has released a list of successful candidates for the Short Service Combatant Course 47/2021. The candidates have been asked to report for officer cadet training at the old site of the Nigerian Defence Academy (NDA), Kaduna, on Tuesday, 6 April, 2021. According to Major General GAT Ochigbano, Military Secretary (Army), the candidates who fail to report by latest 6pm on Wednesday, 7 April, 2021, will forfeit their positions and be replaced by candidates on the Reserve List. The successful candidates were directed to report with the following: Below is a full list of shortlisted candidates:        